Sentencas: A simulation package for the impedance response of SOFC anodes is presented here.
Titulo: Electrochemical Impedance Modeling of a Solid Oxide Fuel Cell Anode

Sentencas: The model couples the gas transport in gas channels and within a porous electrode with the electrochemical kinetics.
Titulo: Electrochemical Impedance Modeling of a Solid Oxide Fuel Cell Anode

Sentencas: The gas phase mass transport is modeled using mass conservation equations.
Titulo: Electrochemical Impedance Modeling of a Solid Oxide Fuel Cell Anode

Sentencas: A transmission line model (TLM), which is suitably modified to account for the electrode microstructural details, is used for modeling the impedance arising from the electrochemical reactions.
Titulo: Electrochemical Impedance Modeling of a Solid Oxide Fuel Cell Anode

Sentencas: In order to solve the system of nonlinear equations, an in-house code based on the finite difference method was developed.
Titulo: Electrochemical Impedance Modeling of a Solid Oxide Fuel Cell Anode

Sentencas: Some of the model constants have been calibrated against experimental data.
Titulo: Electrochemical Impedance Modeling of a Solid Oxide Fuel Cell Anode

Sentencas: It is demonstrated that the simulation tool is capable of predicting the impedance response of an experimental data set obtained on symmetrical cells with Ni/ScYSZ SOFC anodes.
Titulo: Electrochemical Impedance Modeling of a Solid Oxide Fuel Cell Anode

Sentencas: A parametric study is also carried out using the developed simulation tool and the results are further discussed.
Titulo: Electrochemical Impedance Modeling of a Solid Oxide Fuel Cell Anode
